[node name="Level10" type="Node3D"]
editor_description = "Room 10 — Grand Finale. Every trigger type plus both signature obstacles from the level roadmap: FloorNear -> a 6m pit (needs a Final Kick burst, like Room 05) -> FloorFar -> a RotatingGate-guarded gap (needs Overcharge timing, like Room 06) -> FinalFloor. Gear1/Gear2 near, Vial1/WireNode1 mid, Gear3/Vial2 in the last chamber — 6 required objects total, one of each type on both sides of the gate. GREYBOX FIRST PASS — pit width, gate timing and the final chamber's difficulty are all unverified, expect heavy retuning once someone's actually played the full run."

